name: teleport
effect: Does nothing. Wild battles end immediately.
short_effect: Immediately ends wild battles. No effect otherwise.

flavor_text.sun-moon: Use it to flee from any wild Pokémon.
flavor_text.ultra-sun-ultra-moon: Use it to flee from any wild Pokémon.
flavor_text.lets-go-pikachu-lets-go-eevee: The user switches places with a different Pokémon instantly, using telekinetic power.
